### VLab — Labs & Assignments API Tests
### Covers: categories, labs, assignments (group + user)
### Run: npm run dev (port 8800)

@base = http://localhost:8800
@api  = {{base}}/api

@adminEmail    = admin@vlab.com
@adminPassword = admin123

# Update these after creating records
@categoryId  = 1
@labId       = 1
@groupId     = 2
@userId      = 3
@assignId    = 1


###
# ============================================================
# AUTH
# ============================================================

### Login — admin
POST {{api}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}


###
# ============================================================
# CATEGORIES
# ============================================================

### List all categories
GET {{api}}/labs/categories

###

### Create category
POST {{api}}/labs/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "路由交换"
}

###

### Update category
PUT {{api}}/labs/categories/{{categoryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "路由交换（更新）"
}

###

### Delete category
DELETE {{api}}/labs/categories/{{categoryId}}


###
# ============================================================
# LABS
# ============================================================

### List all labs (admin sees all; regular user sees group's labs only)
GET {{api}}/labs

###

### Get lab by ID
GET {{api}}/labs/{{labId}}

###

### Create lab
POST {{api}}/labs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Linux基础实验",
  "description": "掌握Linux基本命令操作",
  "link": "https://docs.example.com/linux-lab",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "vmIds": ["vm-13", "vm-15"]
}

###

### Update lab
PUT {{api}}/labs/{{labId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Linux基础实验（更新）",
  "description": "更新描述",
  "link": "https://docs.example.com/linux-lab-v2",
  "categoryId": {{categoryId}},
  "vmIds": ["vm-13", "vm-15"]
}

###

### Delete lab (fails if active assignments exist)
DELETE {{api}}/labs/{{labId}}


###
# ============================================================
# ASSIGNMENTS — Lab <-> Group
# ============================================================

### List all assignments
GET {{api}}/assign

###

### Assignments for a specific group
GET {{api}}/assign/group/{{groupId}}

###

### Assign lab to group — creates assignment + clones VMs for all group members (streams ndjson)
POST {{api}}/assign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "labId": {{labId}},
  "groupId": {{groupId}}
}

###

### Assign lab to a single user — clones VMs for that user only (streams ndjson)
POST {{api}}/assign/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "labId": {{labId}},
  "userId": {{userId}}
}

###

### Delete assignment — streams ndjson (powers off + deletes VMs, cleans DB)
DELETE {{api}}/assign/{{assignId}}
